description: For sale: $99,900. Small hobby farm on 5 acre corner lot. 2 bedroom/ 1.5 bathroom home with updated eat-in kitchen (updated appliances, new countertops, new cabinets, new flooring. Original part of the house was built in 1940. Living room addition was recently added. On the main level you'll have semi open floor plan, living rm with brand new electric gorgeous fire place, master bedroom with cute half bath. Kitchen with black ash custom cabinets, center island, stainless steel appliances new in 2019. Flooring on the main level new in 2018, Marvin windows. 3 season mud room with full Bath (seasonal use only). On the upper level there are 2 bedrooms with another bdrm/nursery, office/craft area, full bath double sinks. House has forced air heat, furnace new in 2017. You would love the great setting and nice covered porch with 2 decks. Outside you'll have 1+ car garage w/lean to & sauna. Pole shed 40x60 with18x30 finished & heated area + finished room upstairs. Peaceful pond! About 25 ac of hay ground + 5 acres fenced in, nice woods, beautiful trails! Excellent hunting land with deer stands & snowmobiling. Come check it out!
